dagify(c ~ a,
       f ~ c,
       a ~ d,
       c ~ d,
       f ~ d,
       d ~ b + g,
       b ~ e) |>
  ggdag_equivalent_dags(node_size = 10) +
  theme_dag()

dagify(Y ~ X) |>
  ggdag_equivalent_dags() +
  theme_void()

three_var_coords <- read.csv(text = "name,x,y

three_var_coords
